descriptionHtml:
With Grover, you can rent over 2,000 tech products monthly—for a fraction of the purchase price. Forget loans and experience the freedom of renting.

Whether it’s iPhones, MacBooks, or game consoles—rent the tech hits of the most popular brands for 1, 3, 6, or 12 months and send them back for free when the new model comes out. With Grover you always stay up to date with the latest technology and only pay for a device if you actually use it. Outdated technology no longer has to acidify in your drawer and electronic waste is minimized.

Here’s how it works:
1) Choose your desired product and minimum rental period
2) Jump for joy when your Grover package is delivered
3) Prolong flexibly, send back for free, or buy

Your advantages:
2000+ TECH PRODUCTS FROM 10 CATEGORIES
From smartwatches to cameras to tablets—at Grover you’ll find the largest selection of tech devices that you can rent monthly.

NO DEPOSIT, NO HIDDEN COSTS
Simply pay the first month's rent and we’ll ship your device. Of course, the rental doesn’t start until you receive it.

DAMAGE COVERED BY GROVER CARE
If something breaks, we pay 90% and you only pay 10% of the repair or replacement costs. Normal signs of use and device errors are completely covered.

FLEXIBLE RENTAL PERIOD WITH PURCHASE OPTION
Choose a minimum rental period of 1, 3, 6, or 12 months—the longer, the cheaper the monthly price. You can switch to a cheaper term at any time or continue to rent at the same price and cancel monthly. You also have the option to buy the device at any time.

FREE RETURNS
After your minimum rental period has expired, you can cancel your rental at any time. To do this, simply send your product back free of charge one day before the next payment date.

LESS TECH WASTE
Instead of hoarding your purchased technology unused at home as before, simply send your rental products back. We professionally refurbish them for the next renter’s use.

Our tip-top tech promise:
Every device you rent from Grover is either new or like new—and always technically perfect. That’s the Grover Great Condition Promise.

Questions, feedback, or suggestions?
You can reach us anytime at help@grover.com
